Depends: debconf (>= 0.5) | debconf-2.0, ucf (>= 0.28), apache2 | httpd, libapache2-mod-php5, php5-gd, php5-ldap, php5-mysql | php5-pgsql, wwwconfig-common (>= 0.0.37), mysql-client | virtual-mysql-client | postgresql-client, dbconfig-common, php5-cli, ttf-bitstream-vera, ttf-kacst, ${misc:Depends}
Description: an open source web survey application
 Limesurvey is a php web application to perform online suvey.  
 It basically contains everything you need for doing nearly every survey with
 grace. Conditional questions, arrays in various formats, grouping, quotas,
 delegated administration, and much more options.  Note however that it is not
 a result analysis tool (yet).
